DOC.brief_title: Effects Weight Loss Intervention College-age Women
DOC.detailed_description: The purpose study three-fold : 1 ) Determine whether 8-week , patient-centered , weight loss intervention successfully implement overweight , college-age female promotion weight loss prevention weight regain 8-weeks , three month , six month follow-up ; 2 ) Determine effect intervention establish marker calorie restriction , energy expenditure body composition ; 3 ) Determine effect liquid meal physiological subjective marker hunger satiety pre- post- 8wk intervention intervention group vs control group .
